        <div class="footer-top-content">
            <h2 class="company-information-section-title">NON-MEDICAL TRANSPORTATION</h2>
            <h3 class="company-information-title">How Do I Schedule a Ride?</h3>
            <p class="company-information-content collapsed">
                Contact our dispatch services at <a href="tel:<%- company.phone_number_dispatch %>"><%- company.phone_number_dispatch_format %></a>. 
                We are happy to walk you through the process of scheduling trips through our city cab services and our non-medical transportation services.
            </p>
            <button type="button" class="more-info-btn" data-info-btn>
                <div class="more-info-button-icon-wrapper down">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-caret-down-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
