            <h3 class="company-information-title">How Do I Schedule a Ride?</h3>
            <p class="company-information-content collapsed">
                Once approved, please call us at least 48 hours before a scheduled appointment. Reservation hours are from <%- company.business_hours.hours %> <%- company.business_hours.days %> 
